These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: apricot, garlic
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | milk |
| Food       | apricot | garlic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | sprite | coffee |
| Sport      | baseball     | rugby  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, comedy
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, malaysian
1. the chinese is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the chinese is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | comedy  |
| Nationality   | chinese | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
